CrI5r-YXykF3Mu6Oisp1RSuw/KIfWKl4lwKDJ55HVf-e_sySLT8MmMLcx/9" target="_blank"&gt;呼吁棚屋提高利率&lt;/a&gt;以加强日元。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普总统告诉参议院共和党人，&lt;/strong&gt;他对税收法案的40,000美元&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VqB18O6Wc6wVhE36JdpajVCeZz4AG49LFjMA7bbXdh0P1NZ5dfpn7ef6khSwg30X8m8F4D-tYM7f1n3-Llv6jaZIXVm56KQkZ5poKsxQsVo3hfz_K5X6kiqpFBVQlNvrTcshw3iAPo_FSK47YzTvDc8-XuCEXsOyrj1uLIDXM0_b5bP-zYN08WchEyFA62F8bTdLDElBnsKgfWr2JQqvp8fdDJ6yiNs35yYdg0Hqvh5nq0UWjzZ1YkdDgw9zZCgwQrDS8Y9AK3jL5WAHz32TYfhGwQ/O6OcodQAhQZNvrCeFf5CqDtkdmoBau_P/9" target="_blank"&gt;的税收法案&lt;/a&gt;开放。这些评论为参议院共和党努力提出了较低的上限的努力。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BxlngunFNy92j2q0rkXZtTFtPBvXqdnYEC72leCQf1qmtHxitoVMTHPXr8Yr9n66kvxryQbZEmbCwIPzimS9LAqcONilyg2qWT0RIHzSoKbIGsResfDgUOHPr56Jgzau48gFE0W7r11_p1Y2RalZ4ZuMOgQz1i4Zb2MdC2JiWrAHzQbkV5BlnDuMMLmtY6627w99l--Jt0Xi7InoAeWvzDY73ArCOVUgc1Db20z5LHszJ2Q-k4xUaYaiSvFiWRWGEUS8eD0imtIF5Jig5hn8B3asBA/EAlm-5A8FQ_c1rMpjFWEorzhUjXuvOzk/9" target="_blank"&gt;这是一个提醒&lt;/a&gt;法案中的内容。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/loGv4dcN78hcZT0TF8aeM4tOYrHQHvPfNUDGxgpDmqsHKKAMAYqgHxWpEw5i69mhDNqpn7fBz34YiVdvXD0IiHPB_BZzL_koUg1J5tFNUgnrkwuSyRMhpeKyO0QJh1qtjLsNHMbDN8Ya8BxH2UnpdOLra520_NUduyp0IX_b5dyMyOBSrI4e9Bnq8BAZI9lS_VhGxhYwkq4bjBsmAT76yNgPvysUYFRmjOBRuqk3RXi_WZfWlsw-D0oUC_6mRML1ELk12CYTiJsBACjI-3oRVomw_w/kAO2gmhaCKkZ0MYyhgQtSOptT5u-spuB/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/irtMribHP5Q8/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/irtMribHP5Q8/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZ