阿什利写道，该案可能树立先例，正在通过法院努力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/a3CgC5HIO_DIy5nvJga2etdBO7CKUT-stgB4LOJmDScK_StWbrtKuvSaAIE5DFaB7M0SdL90QQd4oULoNNm0j-676Zswu5PivKNLTu9EbcGQ6cQJergATtBIKhnF7IpgDpE3uVogsd1P8kOZymBwMmE-JhjtGDwbkInzMn4CjXqKjygOQw4eA1iVGRAXUuVD0b67HMOGMHJ_763h1GEuqunXXxApgIPrmumvsxDjX4jbwNQBM2LG2hbbaX6TrgawEIVKf4uVnoswEqQQjBGzVze4kw/lVN691Eh-8FFZQGOYcTil3WIG_Su4mPF/9"&gt;注册Soundbite新闻通讯，&lt;/a&gt;以获取有关播客，音乐行业和Ashley Carman的音频趋势的独家报告。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自彭博社的更多信息&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在您的收件箱中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/V2-2LkczkYzKV2yxBxilHMFRzrB_2vqzrS7osFG60soewTkr6kLhoXUPhUM9FBUeNtSKAS_2ov6pYWqBvxOyHFXsU2KdoURby6RYz-lQLlSk0wRf8ooKlZ4M812NZyjeVuSEa7Ms6hhimDYOJNBayl1jLiLqaWQQcwHJzKzyqzIakVjIYHTx96-mRY_XOdMWPSH3p9r5Cehmohntnboy6QwwoWIWstr0fVVCRWznjBpyeuBN6RuymjVAhRhW37cffUfvGah7zX5Z0D09iqnlR1zJ7A/5hbIwTQ_NuYLjLZGeNE48aKW2k8p0JX5/9"&gt;获得深入的技术&lt;/a&gt;和更多彭博技术新闻通讯：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/UKoB3uDCqBnZd37P1wGw7Njo_gwaaY0RI8olMdDROnAStpDVsC1Hvdr20-jsAl1lMc5o611uAyc4w0g8LaAkJqp6bZAEGRr_62jf1tyxLIUNaL7k5kwwqclolKVNu7_49usukn5g2TdIHrhk6S62w_0Na4f6IIzgRv-ok0NEmgh4vD3g7EcoSvRLl6XvYmR0Q5tZmdv5lnNhFAeif0nT4j7ScrHJcY4X9-xeAzF8vw3OBi8gncB3B0jaeujYP9TtiatRFcMFQsDlHxNMmI4JrZ1M5g/eULbc3C2SxDgdSzEMcDzaYuX