60亿美元的赤字。商品和服务的进口在4月下降了16.3％，而出口增长了3％。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/FfJophTIPun8LUKxrNjC83ELJxKyDLCtYNZJYsplcAgVdzmzoq89KHdwcWdEGHrx1osgCT3rjPgX2hyK72qvIksF9kA5xLOHz5LhHmXozem-XTR0OcxcB36ruluLJkrUwupS5W5EBRiZ6qmoSkO58fQHUu0Lwi8PzgKXz1G7XzianyXNwVvlXQUxbJW1ZixkmQHFebUHWSubPPMGs6h-Oq3Yf8AFetINLk0sisZDLOOKVxvas18ZqVwtiTUCT7jDgKS7E5zB7T4CjyD0N65CioLjDA/uXcU92J8UG7ylp-Uu91KZMdms5QTGjvX/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqCuCbpNXhnw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqCuCbpNXhnw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美国劳动力市场的更多坏消息。&lt;/strong&gt;上周为美国失业福利的申请增长至&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qDagC9I3tyO0LlkTMIHs8U6CQwl12zjtkzl__4r3QRP1NomSFEDB50G2uq4Lk1vdeUk5i9XuKdp_5IykqB_hJ8CVYrKA00OUeD3014bAX5YjkRyUKrwd4QHlZXlvOUMARHtzCTXbQOL7rY2w_3S2voK3OhQwJTwRn2nGvrS6xMpnhbf2QEz_YZaV9LHUT5vXhXHNYD6xsegxgy8lYNhxTeoYCuQcZi2hYo63XUHtTWkL7JmGd41HPvfuiY4126WSXTKLhBX2E3LNjTKxMmGmdgc7sQ/uiuXrdLyVec91nve5KV0o1052vmAOgRv/9" target="_blank"&gt;10月以来最高&lt;/a&gt;，这是最近迹象表明&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/6bzFo80NLel9SkDofUQ4rpSM-RJSDmlGyYXygKyR9pLNIhrtoTeTPFQvKavB22CJDqbYx1P6pc9-lUeXDLiVw-m-XU_MboNqp9xyaWsVb6q5YOQ40hp2iSn2RSRpB0ScQ-Q_ECGXqRGCvEWZ1pH6ZOAFTiH4Dw9oY0K6-9_Qj0Wonk2v2iYkvpzFMyH1kszmLqNjFIwGdufSXuEQbXkuhZrEXxIlTj9odhldvEEWhvTM2-4otvmMJFiiK-1mg0sVTVXf0xjNg_NGKinzZg0kcpADOw/MAAzp6YVkL_kA4XEISIXL8MFFG_zWtCS/9" target="_blank"&gt;就业市场正在放缓的&lt;/a&gt;迹象。截至5月31日的一周，最初的索赔提高到247,000。彭博对经济学家的调查中的中位数预测要求235,000份申请。最近的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/UE5NPZ8xrUun-yee6AgvA31jiBgbgkmUvc-SWTHfwWFIy6NvT0ZhakEHR1-LcBP-fK6cCBfRD8WhFYkGoI7qrWS69NfP65IgX3LEkXNDMRSLzScGq4DtnBcoJ7DQ1A9OpHqH6yw3kIlDV_4LjvhhyGzGmWdnniukepisNbqHIu8pavYIoL2IF9UZyx4NCZ6VS2LZg4ftFHj1Q2KetleFc1qEtc_-lErE49-hfBYDZTqI2C1hjMTDgnEWmxriAuJkoO6Icj9-Vs2dP2mgev8MKLjF1A/1IAWy8v6hlaZdf4KE0_bS1OvB2hurYfR/9" target="_blank"&gt;数据&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9dIOahAWgrTRf4EC8e3CE2AydoQkuaGyPH3u39J-jpZA734Mj_vkOMFGeOtoSl4Js7hWlXyu9qaH-xQ1jpjgrhPou-JszRzCfnTlbQRfLu-1FMlMJYJnbfUIiny_tL5TgqQGc_QLmg35BKeaHGHoGqIKogCA5qhsu7DUMd_oE9faZSIXeUDYp33A7ZbX2dffc1t9JfFWWSRQQwLs59ETM6CZD5FyWXRy0Pvcbn21r3YBm1ZjuVLE2U0Vnzqrd4mQh2gAS-5gIFy6X1wHpUaqIM3K2A/mlQIFO2r9BHBoztdQIn8hv1vbh7uqnB_/9" target="_blank"&gt;调查&lt;/a&gt;表明，在接下来的几周内，经济活动的放缓以及福利申请的持续跳跃可能是一个迹象，这可能是更多的美国人很快被解雇。这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ha-7bhT5trGycYuTjkL7GSp-5nGoX-3bqCfyVJhv61CXmpFtT4XDBElfkvQLNCZsqpVCKy6r8e2tcyQiMDeWZb7YWv0uaZG8e7NT6jygJGXi-Q9_3KKr689_kyuNt3azrAGjw46CN1B2m1X8dhvh2TBfvZJr1TeR1uVtCAHVcsGO-5qof0zwKcJTTAS4pPy3aN9033Hj6qCfrzDl9qljtj41Pc8BOF-DQBN2sL1xTumzWWMT8-S8NIrLgCjOC_mTzgul4V-E-m1sOBn5Eg_vDMTyNw/ruZ8yWTPzpBIVB6D4yb30mF25evaYudO/9" target="_blank"&gt;您的市场包装&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a h