pTRrRazwuhCWb0s77ePhw30PvGGQ9gnv2_ozWOfyZRLlH4lwCy15MDnX9W55Ddp-kIaY-5EyeB2DyDGcPPPeMEySiF79y46DYw3UvlSF4WTOhp49QyX7hO8LyKpS4nJaqieCSAkWI08thGqBCfYcZ97vXb7an3ltDTduX4z92IIyKsnJxb70_TFHOCSeKoeox79gXibha20jwHmA/P6fhPAI7LkydaCdnfxoJDWHOFLVYheoa/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNpbqRYPyDF0/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNpbqRYPyDF0/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;德国总理弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;也许寻求一些共同点的领导者&lt;/strong&gt;是德国新安装的校长弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）。他在华盛顿参加了今天与总统的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/w3cUt2Hp_HnowZ77TObHaR_ZF4PFx3bjvmntVwA2q1zMEJR1MlGkQ0L3hLgklBFX0flcI_4tCa8VlMO4SdOJVYGT2CxbthBxlQPUyPfHbQCieWJknE3dIQScpi1Y-pG7l8wOciu_y-K13_7OyHQJO3rIhtqoP35NIOa-_Eu5kH1PxYm1e_T11tXzia_q5DyX8GRnLsDq-fZphjhKq3eaJ-oGEQtl3L9gBT3wZ53y4ShoqSwipfzxXEcffArKHiedwqJDnlvOj6O1PTwhkGw_8u-IqQ/tdEcjelKUNwzDAZPynGskVG7_g0ARX2T/9" target="_blank"&gt;第一次面对面&lt;/a&gt;会议。所有欧洲商品迫在眉睫的税率为50％，时机至关重要。但是德国的问题可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ro9H5H9-RMEkq-N0hBZDcjx9aCG9lktyxr169W8rKtJOFl-xgwec1TdDF0-OhVnent11myztib_57G6CFoUJ3Dn96dFtr7bPhcnrg-Cd2Sij1cOQiZAjYyo-u-xy0nBkHJ28gFMx81LK_bGBXuIKyXshFjNE1XXHw9GlZRjd8P0FSYzMNQv1HyWignkPWtk3JKDTKBybpuGvBjOB3errMyf5xp9Zv7E5ZluKPw-rGLFLDoc9emz5dYe8KufhftERJpSRBDKZMijdijCIPfo6siq2bw/eQOswHCIYHsoxjutkm5y4aW0nQC4FXkS/9" target="_blank"&gt;比特朗普更大&lt;/a&gt;。这提醒您在椭圆形办公室举行的备受瞩目的会议&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/evQwGhKHNWmXZ-ww-bP8L4dv7zrem6h6ssgrBhMoO_WoMNEkUF-YqZY6P7zVTNKKkSmCe0rTFkWR07lkUaTzHjMDaGWhBAK_juTVJtgjSNZYS93oDulA0mVkoQIBEX6VuEI2BbW1A2JvYR-gZTbe9j7PZ51J1G32PWJO_kcjjL4hzvSzltTkGyYFAtxHPB_0E5jfIZL6ASK-KmYPFmdOxxk0vga064YpN1vnoyDp2J8ldsgY7RlKTA05aVck0jsvmMYa-rNMHihmkW3_kG_BJHNUVg/VCxq4cRMliFxZKYC5jRVE1UjX-ztXHg4/9" target="_blank"&gt;可能会出错。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普禁止&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9hxE6mXkOCXYeNPeD41V8CaX2v8GfzlRdGv4oYKcwHZuYxQZayOFLdNR-A5rNAO1tLM_x7U66noK9SzFr4f6ec9lZCIgsqxO3s2sOcIZXC5J6fFUq9FXjYJdsrKgxLwaTrU0qaKTt1urUtcXlJKn740dPPv2fODtCcDtZ9w_4aYiWyJqcCy8iZUxumZzVlPWW9NBTAc4laP3WM_UGoOzxCvFSUEI-2e0BnPDr0x5LYA6wGVYEPeWTRC5ZoHq5_U6tJQgiqjxgldjxn8u_OY1HWM8vQ/oaSf83PlR5a5-qtrCX2aXv2ii3qe6OaX/9" target="_blank"&gt;来自12个国家进入美国的个人&lt;/a&gt;，从他的第一任期起恢复了最有争议的措施之一。这&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LCXNYGaXzwBEhsCLUhayxV4wSAQKJJErOlVFuGBJt8_SKSp-_0nzyCjLPgo_-J0idsdNvFAksr5D1JFTquNburQdfnhcveZAl1VHfJC95YQg8AYX3csH7bPfjVDPwg__YX-dc-yK4O7vnpH2wwS5F7IU1Ivv8_vlB3AS4Xj1O1qpx7YWsxEpZWUn-QkR2YeXzrzpRF0PZzti1i_7awt8mrfzCk3zdzsRT1alJcqaI3pKPebMY_zJsYNyFa1eplXhEdnC4eUrh3q5SotxXJI5IRs8Ag/HbpcpTILyKV90Zicr5ueiVcKMALJQGev/9" target="_blank"&gt;也部分限制了包括古巴和老挝在内的七个国家的人们的进入&lt;/a&gt;。他还签署了一项行政诉讼，该行动阻止外国国民进入美国在哈佛学习。这可能使他的政府&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GXWv9vxMOxHderoB7vcLeCBECuRc8BLNTJeKfm6vo06we1PvveBl2gb4tpjRaQfmFhzaeDXvMC10YDmlDt-xUlkqKB6z7Trl-39gUTwHCGeIRCQZZ_y-jL0vzCVjujjD5i-zg11x-yl-3KgB837w0olZYYb2K3Hxj4rXMD2kADKj2k4ewlQYvkuZVUaqZfWPkd_0s7ohcgaH3Bx_q63UG9_vmdzv_h7__0-p6vvWKtTbr4869V9q1hXe7i9fFLZ6fEpPdD2bWN41Lg6xB3dsN7uQiA/_g4eVm1VLE6lwwNsGD0CMWO2iSHwKV_i/9" target="_blank"&gt;避开了一项裁决&lt;/a&gt;，使大学得以暂时继续入学。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.c