m上与您的朋友和追随者一起&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/DXiDIN4wKazaPBQDlPbczs8vkuXHb8NXn_k940X6jKIl554aB5p672r_S329J0O-r93xmy_ilAvdRLWOR06SB9quBu47uBn5OVl_dS_vGWfwJvsNXbS0O2FsS-_PfLlfMdcaaigsjT41583-91Dwg_qSvSlw4w2B72OWPe-4TplCwDVX6d-WLMlpYObhn2B-vMfBA1_6c-WYlT_XI1SexDr6UGSjuW0rm_xfOe587w-gFloV8ab44WpN8StB5w0pOnpmNEk9TrqmXUidhGC2-QbmUA/PNCO8Krfyp4fWB5Hb0AnA8fVy6D0cLIa/9" target="_blank"&gt;阅读并分享完整的故事&lt;/a&gt;。有关无限制的气候和能源新闻， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lfMz6IPNzYSVW_GcuiTNvbAvbqrkr3b0DawZGfqtv_Q6OUMWSi5xeI9kFdNvW7z6ZUa_8JNMK3Fvrlxsb5i2XPwR7Ez2z_zpDroPkcFcBPaBkBzwZlZ4bR3XBxHXR9lZ-XE2rKzzQSjkv9vvqs7GmRCjVWQRha_NXSYuLdsbGezcJpOV9ndcv88ZBcPWY8R2gsZWJSzOf0z7OVpFNst4FO9au31ToTUZYOxcZT0zRQrI6138nEosorAHhYglV9KiFw_W3nR9WC40O6VVSJN75bqxJA/38diwBVaofG8Zk6GHZw3VtkslETHDxb7/9"&gt;请订阅&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;帮助我们改善彭博新闻通讯： &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ofNYv-MmcXOhmPeJ9crmHADuEn9Mtnz40TEwtGwXCwI7ojZPUGKWx6_9Dsh2nc1jhU_juVJvo3-fYExWFPWBXHABx83nDlBVAsPeFvW87WpZMCV0qaaMO5IqNTOsLrNENShnOPRxnnrI-1fS3xM9AtLs7Gw0NFmt5oF9N2LPV2QZQHMtL71btRPDfr9rkN0ig4ocbCFdipIMcJPrhJUr-xnFC6vj0T98lWQm6W8zYQgAJJj7gPOG2PZxSZHhWLohZ1KlqNGHsMGk8B-ZGqOvlVQYFhb3avJv_tG4hT9hzhK3d0d6a3vtADR4LoXrufgXpGqVk1Eu6wGerWPJcDxFlcieqP2XMNwMP5U08vRriV3qG5VUmELNGQ/Y3b5BNEr5W11wrtNra_MzTQIE0HxXgf0/9"&gt;进行快速调查&lt;/a&gt;，分享您对您的注册体验以及将来希望看到的想法。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;失踪的工程师&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border